                    <h2 class="main-title">Radigone® Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p>
                        Thank you for using our Services. At Radigone, we believe you should get to choose when your information is shared, which is one of the reasons we have created a platform where you can get paid for watching ads and sharing your information!

                        Radigone (“<b>Radigone</b>”) operates the Radigone mobile application (“<b>App</b>”), the Radigone.com website (“<b>Site</b>”), and the pay-for-views in form of Radigone points and Bank transfer services offered through our platform (together with the App and the Sites), the (“Services”).

                        Radigone respects and protects the privacy of our users.  We maintain strict policies to ensure the privacy of those who use our Services. This policy (“Privacy Policy”) describes the types of information we may collect from you and our practices for how we collect, use, maintain, protect, and disclose such information. The way that we collect and use your information depends on the way you access the Services (whether by Site or by App). This Privacy Policy also includes a description of certain rights that you may have over information that we may collect from you.

                        By using the Services, you agree to this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with our policies and practices, your choice is to not use our Services.
                    </p>
                    <h3>Why we have a Privacy Policy?</h3>
                    <p>
                        The reason behind putting up the Privacy Policy is so that you may go through it and adhere to the norms of our policies. This helps us serve you better on the Radigone and their sponsor’s Offers and Benefits websites. It gives you an insight on how we operate. If you are not clear on any of the points in the policy, you may always get in touch with us and have your doubts clarified.
                    </p>
                    <h3>INFORMATION Radigone®  COLLECTS AND HOW WE COLLECT IT</h3>
